From 854009849235308d1319cf4f8ff52f00a3b07026 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Thong Thai <thong.thai@amd.com>
Date: Thu, 15 Aug 2019 14:00:30 -0400
Subject: drm/amdgpu: enable VCN DPG for Renoir
Git-commit: 854009849235308d1319cf4f8ff52f00a3b07026
Patch-mainline: v5.4-rc1
References: bsc#1152489

This will enable indirect SRAM loading for VCN DPG mode initialization.

Signed-off-by: Thong Thai <thong.thai@amd.com>
Reviewed-by: Leo Liu <leo.liu@amd.com>
Reviewed-by: Prike Liang <Prike.Liang@amd.com>
Signed-off-by: Alex Deucher <alexander.deucher@amd.com>
Acked-by: Thomas Zimmermann <tzimmermann@suse.de>
---
 drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/soc15.c | 4 +++-
 1 file changed, 3 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/soc15.c b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/soc15.c
index 1a8ffed6b02c..53f21c567e97 100644
--- a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/soc15.c
+++ b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/soc15.c
@@ -1174,7 +1174,9 @@ static int soc15_common_early_init(void *handle)
 				 AMD_CG_SUPPORT_ATHUB_LS |
 				 AMD_CG_SUPPORT_ATHUB_MGCG |
 				 AMD_CG_SUPPORT_DF_MGCG;
-		adev->pg_flags = AMD_PG_SUPPORT_SDMA;
+		adev->pg_flags = AMD_PG_SUPPORT_SDMA |
+				 AMD_PG_SUPPORT_VCN |
+				 AMD_PG_SUPPORT_VCN_DPG;
 		adev->external_rev_id = adev->rev_id + 0x91;
 
 		if (adev->pm.pp_feature & PP_GFXOFF_MASK)
